@startuml
|System|
start

:Verify User Role;

if (Research Student?) then (yes)
    :Load Research Student Dashboard Components;
    :Enable System Functions for Research Student;
else (no)
    :Load Other User Dashboard Components;
    :Enable System Functions for Other User;
endif

:Render Dashboard;
:Open Asset Return Function;

:Check Asset Availability;
 
if (Asset Available?) then (yes)
    :Record Reservation Request;
    :Update Asset Status to Reserved;
    :Update Status Across System;
    :Log Reservation Timestamp;
    :Send Reservation Confirmation Email to User;
    :Reservation Complete; 
else (no)
    :Trigger Asset Unavailable Notification;
    :Reservation Complete;
endif

:Identify Reserved Asset in System;
:Confirm Return in System;
:Update Asset Status to Available;
:Update Status Across Network;
:Clear Reservation Record from User Account;
:Send Return Notification Email (User must return item within X days);
stop
@enduml
